{
  "stem": "11179.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I understand it's really not related.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You only have to go in a few more years, a few more years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We don't have to go in today very much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Unless you want to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the end of the war came [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] kind of unexpected when we heard about the atomic bomb.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard about it, and the word atomic bomb was mentioned, and we-- we asked the engineer for-- for my boss.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we-- we asked him, is there such thing?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said-- he thought it was just a very powerful bomb.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't think it was atomic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was-- he just didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when we thought it was over, there were certain-- it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The police was gone for a while, and there was some kind of a riot, some-- some Jewish people whose friends or family were killed by the Japanese.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Particularly, there was-- there were a couple of Russian policeman still at the police who turned them in because they came late, or when they had a passport to leave, they came late over the border.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I did not mention-- unfortunately, there was really no time-- the-- the-- the Japanese police and Mr.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Ghoya, who called himself the King of the Jews and who gave those permissions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this is a chapter in itself again, which-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] those people any-- anyway, it was a lot of chicanery there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they wanted to get even, particularly wanted to get those two Russian policeman.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this was after the first time, after the first bomb, which was-- was it Nagasaki or Iwo-- Iwo Jima?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not sure which one was the first one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We know there were two.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
